    ∇ r←GetRefTo nsname;name
     ⍝ Get a reference to a container namespace (or ⍬ if that is not possible)
     
      :If ~(⊂nsname)∊'⎕SE'(,'#')
          r←⍬ ⍝ pessimism in action
